messages.message:
Great feedback definitely aligns with roadmap and planned improvements!

@Kaustubh (KD) and @jack.robbins it would be good to create backlog EPD tickets for project versioning and review rejection workflow if they don't exist already! Feels like we're getting enough signal on both to consider prioritizing for Q4.

Quick question on (4) though - do they plan to use human review or would this be a classification validation?  Wondering whether those rules are things the human reviewers would know and reject if they see it or if we'd need to codify at the class level and show as classification validation in human review which would trigger the human review to reject?
